node.text:
It comes from setting intentions, being authentic , putting in work and having a support system to push you to your FULL potential. 

When I started writing the blueprint for the DNCR Academy a few years ago i knew it needed to be more than tutorials because becoming a dancer is so much more than just learning steps. 

It needed to be a community, a family of people around the world that support each other and hold each other accountable.  We've only been open 3 weeks and it's crazy what you guys have already accomplished!  Overcoming fears, booking jobs, growing on social media, learning choreo you never thought possible. 

We have everyone from 4 year olds, to parents, grandparents, people that have never danced in their lives and some of the best dancers in the world, all in the same group pushing each other.  It's amazing to watch and I'm honored to be a part of it.

If you're looking for something to level up your training or just want to have fun and feel comfortable to be yourself, it's all love here.  Happy monday, let's get it this week 💙 @dncracademy 

#DNCRfam  www.dncr.com
